o good and evil. We are all made the same. We can be the camp guard or the prisoner given the circumstances. We could have chosen the power to kill in lieu of surviving the worst of the concentration camps. It is built in our genetic code. This makes sense as evil becomes necessary at tinmes. When the threat of harm to another love one bestows infront of us, we will not hesitate to defend or create violence. </p>","excerpt":"Adolf Hitler  pushed humanity to the edge during World War 2. This was the period where violence became necessary, tremendous cooperation to…","fields":{"tagSlugs":["/tags/charles-darwin/","/tags/jordan-b-peterson/","/tags//"]},"frontmatter":{"title":"Born Good and Evil / Blog#0025","tags":["Charles Darwin","Jordan B. Peterson",null],"date":"March 01, 2019"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/born-good-and-evil/"}}